Published Friday, 2026-02-27, including PRs merged Friday, 2026-02-06 through Thursday, 2026-02-12.
íŸ@b0054f48e983ebea194eaeb7e06744b219797ee3312cb19c7a1e167962ebffe1⁄Title: title: 'This week in Nushell #338'
Path: Nushell
Content:
@fdncred:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17555] cleaned up ansi command pr.md (#17555)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17533] added 
``nu``
 to the ignore_list for 
``:try``
 in 
``explore``
 (#17533)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17532] disabled auto tail and tracked previous row count in push_layer in explore (#17532)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17516] updated to latest reedline commit bdcc842 (#17516)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17514] updated structured ansi to support attr names and codes (#17514)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17511] updated nushell to reedline to 4c16687 (#17511)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17446] made 
``let``
 pass-thru in mid pipeline, output no values when assigned at beginning of the pipeline, output values at the end of the pipeline (#17446)
@blindFS:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17553] fixed block duplication for aliased ones only in 
``replace_in_variable``
 (#17553)
@WindSoilder:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17551] updated uu libs to 0.6.0 (#17551)
@jlcrochet:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17550] removed 
``$env.config.input_list``
 from 
``input list``
 (#17550)
@Juhan280:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17549] aligned --tmpdir behavior in 
``mktemp``
 with coreutils/uutils (#17549)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17540] added 
``path_columns``
 to PipelineMetadata for flexible path rendering (#17540)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17508] added linewise and non-blank start edit commands (#17508)
@evolvomind:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17547] fixed variable expansion inconsistency in path arguments for commands using GlobPattern (#17547)
@monigarr:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17545] improved strings command help text (PR 9 of 10) (#17545)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17544] improved math random help text (PR 8 of 10) (#17544)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17528] improved help text for filesystem, path, and platform commands (PR 7 of 10) (#17528)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17523] improved help text for bytes, conversions, database, and date commands (#17523)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17522] improved help text for format commands (PR 4 of 10) (#17522)
@maxim-uvarov:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17539] avoided panic in replace_in_variable for permanent blocks (#17539)
@cablehead:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17537] deprecated 
``metadata set --merge``
 in favor of closure form (#17537)
@InnocentZero:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17526] added skip columns functionality (#17526)
@cuiweixie:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17521] fixed median calculation to use sorted len (#17521)
@weirdan:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17519] fixed poll/pool typo for 
``http pool``
 (#17519)
@hustcer:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17517] upgraded interprocess to 2.3.1 (#17517)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17506] pinned libc and interprocess to fix cross-platform build failures (#17506)
@BluewyDiamond:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17509] made 
``rm``
 behavior consistent with 
``mv``
, 
``du``
, and 
``cp``
 (#17509)
@stuartcarnie:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17491] enabled OSC133 click events via reedline (#17491)
@app/dependabot:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17541] bumped crate-ci/typos from 1.43.1 to 1.43.4 (#17541)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17495] bumped git2 from 0.20.0 to 0.20.4 (#17495)
