@NiltonVolpato:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/reedline/pull/1014] added 
``libc``
 feature to enable crossterm's libc backend (#1014)
@schlich:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/reedline/pull/963] improved CONTRIBUTING.md to more closely match CI execution (#963)
